          { "feature": "cotton_wool_spots", "weight": 2 },
          { "feature": "no_neovascularization", "weight": 5 }
        ],
        "management": "Optimize glycemic control (HbA1c target <7%). Blood pressure control. Lipid management. Annual dilated retinal exam. If severe NPDR: consider panretinal photocoagulation (PRP)."
