          { "feature": "cystoid_macular_edema_on_OCT", "weight": 5 },
          { "feature": "blurred_central_vision", "weight": 5 }
        ],
        "management": "Anti-VEGF injections (Ranibizumab, Aflibercept, Bevacizumab) monthly or treat-and-extend. Focal/grid laser for non-center involving DME. Steroid implants (Ozurdex, Iluvien) for chronic cases."
